					<outline text="&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.wikiart.org/en/rene-magritte/georgette-magritte-1934&quot;&gt;Georgette Magritte&lt;/a&gt;, 1934." created="Wed, 26 Jul 2023 12:48:26 GMT" inlineImage="https://imgs.scripting.com/2023/07/26/georgetteMagritte.png"/>
