			<outline text="July 25" created="Tue, 25 Jul 2023 12:25:44 GMT" type="calendarDay" name="25">
				<outline text="This is the &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/scripting/sourceNamespaceComments&quot;&gt;place&lt;/a&gt; for questions about the &lt;a href=&quot;http://source.scripting.com/&quot;&gt;Source namespace&lt;/a&gt;." created="Tue, 25 Jul 2023 13:07:21 GMT" type="outline"/>
				<outline text="How exactly does MuskCo get people to say X instead of Twitter? Has Google gotten any recognition for Alphabet. Has Facebook got anyone beyond a few reporters to say Meta? I call bullshit. The name is Twitter." created="Tue, 25 Jul 2023 12:25:45 GMT" type="outline"/>
