				<outline text="An &lt;a href=&quot;http://scripting.com/2023/07/24/mantonVoicemail.m4a&quot;&gt;open voicemail&lt;/a&gt; to &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.google.com/search?q=site%3Ascripting.com+manton+reece&quot;&gt;Manton Reece&lt;/a&gt;, developer of &lt;a href=&quot;https://micro.blog/&quot;&gt;micro.blog&lt;/a&gt;, about creating a common API for social media apps." created="Mon, 24 Jul 2023 12:08:46 GMT" type="outline" enclosure="http://scripting.com/2023/07/24/mantonVoicemail.m4a" enclosureType="audio/mp3" enclosureLength="6824970"/>
